      <lemma xml:id="lem-direct-product-group">
        <statement>
          <p>
            Let <m>(G,+)</m> and <m>(H,\times)</m> be groups. Then <m>G\times H</m> is a group, where <m>(G\times H,*)</m> denotes the Cartesian Product of <m>G</m> and <m>H</m>, and the operation <m>*</m> is defined 
